Package com.adidas.ui.mailcheck

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MailCheck
    Interface for components which are able to provide suggestion on valid email in case if email passed was mis-spelled.
    MailCheckConfiguration
    Configuration for mailcheck component.
    StringDistanceFunction
    Intereface for implementations of string distance functions to use for mailcheck logic: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Levenshtein_distance
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultMailCheck
    Default implementation of mailcheck component.
    DefaultMailCheckConfiguration
    Default implementation of MailCheckConfiguration used inside of this package.
    DefaultStringDistanceFunction
    Default implementation of string distance function used inside of this package: http://siderite.blogspot.com/2007/04/super-fast-and-accurate-string- distance.html.
    MailCheckFactory
    Creates an instance of mailcheck component using default configuration and string distance functions.
    MailCheckSuggestion
    Holds result of mailcheck suggestion logic execution.
    SuggestionFormatter
    Helper class to format e-mail formatted suggestions.
